You are here: SALESFORCE HELP DOCS ANALYTICS Set Up Einstein Discovery

Set up permissions in enable users in your org to use Einstein Discovery. Monitor usage statistics.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition.
Einstein Discovery requires either the CRM Analytics Plus license or the Einstein Predictions license.

Permission Sets and Permissions for Einstein Discovery
The CRM Analytics Plus license provides standard permission sets and permissions that you can assign to user accounts.
Assign multiple permission sets to an individual user account.
